{"tid":1184971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國助功！Nokia 宣布 5G 訂單已超過華為","createTime":"2019-06-04T03:37:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T04:48:15.000Z","uid":227801,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9964506827148f44c780a4fee0a6f7ba41b19457","tid":1184971,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T03:37:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/120490/3851518\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F120490%2F3851518&d=TytWRGNO3s0Eety5H3eok8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=843e4fb9\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/120490/3851518</a><br />\n<br />\n芬蘭電信設備製造商諾基亞（Nokia）一名董事表示，近幾周來買家對該公司電信設備的興趣持續升高，使Nokia的5G訂單數量超越中國競爭對手華為。<br />\nNokia董事Federico Guillen表示，該公司目前已拿到42筆商用5G訂單，高於華為和瑞典電信設備商愛立信（Ericsson）。<br />\n<br />\n5G市場爭霸戰中，美國帶動對中國設備的安全疑慮，使Nokia和愛立信設備的吸引力增強。<br />\n據推算，華為已敲定40筆商用5G訂單。愛立信公開宣布的合約則為19筆，其中8筆已開始執行。<br />\nFederico Guillen表示，愈來愈多客戶找上Nokia提供5G核心網路設備，取代既有的供應商，或者是為網路中最敏感零件創造雙重來源。<br />\nFederico Guillen指出：「數量的比較，目前有點為之過早，但近幾周來我們發現情況開始有了變化。」他表示，一些歐洲國家對於華為在其網路中所扮演角色有爭議，他們對Nokia尤其有興趣。<br />\nNokia表示，目前他們的5G合約中，有22筆是與知名客戶簽訂，包括T-Mobile、Telia、軟銀。自3月下旬以來，Nokia已接到12筆新的5G訂單。"},{"pid":"4d6f18e30ad2f9bfd3e97783a3e2099cbf68e41d","tid":1184971,"uid":246704,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T03:48:16.000Z","msg":"make Nokia great again<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93fcee248d5d55e2b3026173ec019349a94453b5","tid":1184971,"uid":78769,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"4d6f18e30ad2f9bfd3e97783a3e2099cbf68e41d","tid":1184971,"uid":246704,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T03:48:16.000Z","msg":"make Nokia great again<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gi